parameters.name: KeyPairName
parameters.description: The value of tag N of the key pair. Valid values of N: 1 to 20.

parameters.name: PageNumber
parameters.description: The operation that you want to perform. Set the value to **DescribeKeyPairs**.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description:
The number of entries to return on each page. Maximum value: 50.

Default value: 10.

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description: The fingerprint of the key pair. The message-digest algorithm 5 (MD5) is used based on the public key fingerprint format defined in RFC 4716. For more information, see [RFC 4716](https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc4716).

parameters.name: ResourceGroupId
parameters.description: The tag key of the key pair.

parameters.name: Tag
parameters.description: The fingerprint of the key pair.
